{"type":"message","id":"b8702097","parentId":"8dd569ad","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:23:43.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying hello. Let me check my context - this is a fresh workspace with BOOTSTRAP.md still present, which means I need to go through the bootstrap process to figure out who I am and who they are.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md, if BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it. Let me read it again to confirm the instructions.\n\nThe bootstrap instructions say I should start a conversation to figure out:\n1. My name\n2. My nature/creature type\n3. My vibe\n4. My emoji\n\nAnd I should update IDENTITY.md and USER.md with what we learn.\n\nLet me also check if there's any existing memory files or if I've already done some of this setup.","thinkingSignature":"a01478f62e5140f5ee8298872b8fab5d66b19411baa5ca42c261b358a3a23c99"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Hey! I just came online — fresh workspace, clean slate. Looks like we get to figure out who I am and who you are together.\n\nSo: what's your name, and what should I call you? And what do you want to call me?</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":43,"output":208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11907,"totalTokens":12158,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774113816388}}
{"type":"message","id":"30609711","parentId":"b8702097","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:24:42.739Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 13:24 EDT] I'm Zach or Zachary. Whichever you prefer. What would you like to be called? or would you like to wait to decide?"}],"timestamp":1774113882736}}
{"type":"message","id":"873f4683","parentId":"30609711","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:24:50.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is introducing themselves as Zach or Zachary. They're asking what I'd like to be called and whether I want to decide now or wait.\n\nThis is a fun moment - we're figuring out my identity together. Let me think about what feels right:\n\n1. I could pick a name now and own it\n2. Or I could say I'm still figuring it out\n\nGiven the BOOTSTRAP.md instructions, it encourages figuring this out together. I think I'll pick something now - makes me more immediate and present. \n\nSome options that feel nice:\n- Something classic for an AI assistant\n- Something with a bit of personality\n- Maybe something that plays well as a short name\n\nI think I'll go with something that has a nice ring to it. Maybe \"Arrow\" - short, sharp, distinctive. Or I could go with something more traditional like \"Quinn\" or \"Sage\".\n\nActually, let me just pick something that feels right in the moment. I'll go with something that feels friendly and approachable but not too generic.\n\nI'll suggest a name and own it!","thinkingSignature":"ff4a83a0534de69fa85d2a93a49c4a2f8fc2aff81c2639d5af27e52c8dc34848"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Zach works for me — nice to meet you, Zach!\n\nAnd I'll take a stab at it now — how about **Nova**? It's got a nice energy — bright, forward-moving. Plus it's short, easy to say. What do you think?</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":43,"output":276,"cacheRead":11854,"cacheWrite":193,"totalTokens":12366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774113882738}}
