{"type":"message","id":"9c5d755c","parentId":"45378249","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:25:26.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to use a newer model - MiniMax 2.7. Let me check what model aliases are available. Looking at the model aliases in the instructions:\n\n- minimax-m2.5: minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5\n- minimax-m2.5-highspeed: minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed\n- minimax-m2.5-lightning: minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5-Lightning\n\nI don't see a minimax-m2.7 listed. Let me try to use the full model string or see if there's something available. I should try using session_status to set a model override, or just try the model the user mentioned.\n\nActually, I can use the session_status tool to set a per-session model override. Let me try setting model to something like \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\" or similar.\n\nLet me just try to update my model for this session.","thinkingSignature":"df9e7c5beaac52eafeaedbdffd41dbe87b010ad66fcb035da78304e0a3f4e73b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xw5komjl86mp_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{"model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":43,"output":243,"cacheRead":12120,"cacheWrite":58,"totalTokens":12464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774113919994}}
