{"type":"message","id":"eba18a9e","parentId":"6f05f699","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:54:01.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The insight discovery ran and found 151 insights. Most of the top insights are showing `nan` values, which means the experiment data has a lot of missing values. The strongest non-nan insight is:\n- Strong correlation (0.776) between duration_seconds and metrics.p99_latency_improvement_percent — this suggests longer experiments tend to show better latency improvements\n\nThe `nan` values in the optimal configurations suggest that the experiment data has a lot of missing values, which makes the analysis less useful.\n\nLet me now look at the results more carefully. The key findings from the three experiments are:\n\n1. **Counterintuitive hypotheses**: 7/7 confirmed - all counterintuitive hypotheses were validated\n\n\n2. **Compound experiments**: Found 6 synergies and 9 counterintuitive findings across 32 combinations tested\n3. **Insight discovery**: 151 insights but mostly `nan` values due to missing data, with one strong correlation between experiment duration and latency improvement\n\nThe main takeaway is that these findings need validation in real-world conditions. Now I should update my memory with what we've discovered and share these results with Zach.","thinkingSignature":"5a4672c0fbcdb1532d0e96413480be6b22dfb75713a668ba886830e14b891afb"},{"type":"text","text":"All three experiments completed. Let me read the full results:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0n6v6lxz7rtc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:/dev/EXP && python -X utf8 -c \"\nimport json\n# Read and summarize all three experiment results\nprint('=== COUNTERINTUITIVE HYPOTHESES ===')\nwith open('results/counterintuitive/counterintuitive_results_20260321_135202.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\nfor h in data.get('hypotheses', [])[:3]:\n    print(f'  {h[\\\"hypothesis_name\\\"]}: confirmed={h.get(\\\"confirmed\\\")}, conf={h.get(\\\"confidence\\\")}')\n\nprint()\nprint('=== COMPOUND BREAKTHROUGH ===')\nwith open('results/compound_experiments/breakthrough_report_20260321_135324.json') as f:\n    br = json.load(f)\nprint(f'  Synergies: {br.get(\\\"synergies_found\\\", 0)}')\nprint(f'  Counterintuitive: {br.get(\\\"counterintuitive_findings\\\", 0)}')\nprint(f'  Top synergies:')\nfor s in br.get('top_synergies', [])[:5]:\n    print(f'    {s}')\n\nprint()\nprint('=== INSIGHT DISCOVERY ===')\nwith open('results/insights/insight_report_20260321_135345.json') as f:\n    ir = json.load(f)\nprint(f'  Total insights: {ir.get(\\\"total_insights\\\", 0)}')\nfor i in ir.get('top_insights', [])[:5]:\n    print(f'    {i[\\\"type\\\"]}: {i[\\\"description\\\"]}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68732,"output":616,"cacheRead":11874,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81222,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774115625457}}
